{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_00.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br><i>In a world where technology has become an integral part of corporate governance, and megacities have turned into a mix of concrete jungles and cyber-reality, looms a city full of violence and murder.<br><br>Amidst this chaos, only one force fights for order. They are the faceless guardians of the law, the keepers of order - executioners. Take on the role of a law executioner and restore law and order in this city.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/title_01_english.png?t=1729153691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_01.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br>Choose starting gear that suits your playstyle. Special stimulants used in combat can tilt the battle in your favor. Bullets with incendiary or paralyzing effects will help deal with the most dangerous enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/title_02_english.png?t=1729153691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_02.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br>Assessing the battlefield, pick optimal positions, and manipulate enemy placement for better outcomes. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/title_03_english.png?t=1729153691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_03.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br>Level architecture and enemy placement vary, presenting new challenges upon replay.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/title_04_english.png?t=1729153691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_04.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br>Each subsequent enemy kill allows you to reuse your abilities. Strategic moves enable you to dispatch of multiple foes in one turn.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/title_05_english.png?t=1729153691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/extras/gif_05.gif?t=1729153691\" /><br>Each extension of your turn triggers a timer, during which you must decide your next move.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">And remember! If one executioner falls, another will take his place!</h2>If you make a mistake or face failure, there's always a chance to try again. Justice in the law comes with a stern hand. And you are the law!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Something went off plan.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2876850/9917f5b37539c4cc4d45175270d90f0e9893213d.jpg"},{"name":"I'll be back!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2876850/2545d5d34eef9d3a56aff3ffd1774333551bcc50.jpg"},{"name":"Novice Tactician.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2876850/13b9910a72215c76c00c675a2de16816c61ddde7.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729153691","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729153691","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/1c11d6edfbce8984f02f88a2144c3c9632a71a06/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729153691","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876850/1c11d6e